Package: nycOpenData
Type: Package
Title: Easy Access to NYC Open Data APIs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Christian", "Martinez", 
           email = "c.martinez0@outlook.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simple, reproducible access to datasets from 
    the NYC Open Data platform (<https://data.cityofnewyork.us/>). 
    The initial release includes the 'nyc_311()' function for retrieving 
    311 Service Request data in a tidy format.
